             `(S0, S1, S2, S3, S4, S5)` implements `squealy::InsertSelectRowCompatible<(T0, T1, T2, T3, T4, T5), squealy::TupleRow>`
             `(S0, S1, S2, S3, S4, S5, S6)` implements `squealy::InsertSelectRowCompatible<(T0, T1, T2, T3, T4, T5, T6), squealy::TupleRow>`
